  "Description": {
    "English": "An upgrade to the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Minotaur</span> Heavy Exocraft Hybrid, the Liquidator is a cutting-edge heavy-duty combat unit, designed to operate in the harshest of environments.<br><br>Will function as a semi-autonomous <span class=\"name name-technology\">artificial pilot plugin</span>. Installation allows the Minotaur to <span class=\"name name-stellar\">traverse planets itself</span> and engage in <span class=\"name name-stellar\">combat</span> or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">mining</span> activities to support its primary operator.<br><br>The AI pilot will always cede control to the primary operator when they enter the cockpit.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "作为<span class=\"name name-technology\">弥诺陶洛斯</span>重型混合强化艇的升级版本，清算员是一种尖端的重装作战单元，并且被设计成能够在最险恶的环境中执行任务。<br><br>能够作为半自主<span class=\"name name-technology\">智能导航插件</span>使用。安装后，弥诺陶洛斯将能够<span class=\"name name-stellar\">自主跨越行星</span>，并在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交战</span>或<span class=\"name name-stellar\">采矿</span>作业中辅助主要操作员。<br><br>当主要操作员进入驾驶舱后，人工智能将移交设备控制权。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "清算人是一種尖端耐用戰鬥機體，為<span class=\"name name-technology\">彌諾陶洛斯</span>重型混合強化艇的升級，專為在最嚴苛的環境中運作而設計。<br><br>可作為半自主的<span class=\"name name-technology\">人工駕駛員外掛程式</span>使用。安裝後能讓彌諾陶洛斯<span class=\"name name-stellar\">獨自穿越星球</span>並進行<span class=\"name name-stellar\">戰鬥</span>或者<span class=\"name name-stellar\">採礦</span>活動，以支援其主要操作員。<br><br>主要操作員進入駕駛艙後，人工駕駛員將會交付控制權。"
  },
